Global Bulk Explosives Market Insights
Bulk Explosives Market size was valued at USD 11.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 18.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Bulk Explosives Market Overview
The bulk explosives market size was valued at USD 23.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2025 to 2032. This growth is driven by rising demand in mining and construction activities, where bulk explosives are increasingly used for blasting and excavation. As the construction industry experiences an uptick globally, the market for bulk explosives continues to expand. Additionally, technological advancements in the production of safer and more efficient explosives contribute to market growth. However, strict government regulations and safety concerns are key challenges that could influence market dynamics.

